              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/14172846/" class="">第99页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/shanzhongqiya/" class=" " title="东未明">东未明</a>
                (花心轻拆，露滴牡丹开)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="14172846">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">可以生死与共，去无法一起看朝阳升起，但是你们一定能走下去……</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-08-18 11:52</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                可以生死与共，去无法一起看朝阳升起，但是你们一定能走下去……
